---
title: Haloumi Butter Masala & Rice with Crushed Peanuts & Baby Leaves
description: One haloumi masala coming right up! Squeaky haloumi is being added to a fantastic creamy masala because we just know when
it joins the veggies, the curry sauce and fluffy rice there will be magic in the air.

